  "instructions": [
    "Drain firm tofu and press gently to remove excess water.",
    "In a small bowl, mix red food coloring with 10 drops of water for even distribution.",
    "Blend tofu, lemon juice, garlic, dill, salt, and pepper until smooth.",
    "Slowly add the red food coloring mixture to the tofu blend, stirring until fully incorporated.",
    "Pour the mixture onto toasted bread slices and let it set for 2 minutes.",
    "Serve immediately for a cozy, bitter-creamy experience."
